WEBVTT

00:06.093 --> 00:08.617
I told Isabelle
I'd drop you off at the nest.

00:08.747 --> 00:10.053
She'll come looking
for you there.

00:10.227 --> 00:11.359
Man: [Indistinct] made it
out of the city

00:11.489 --> 00:12.664
with your
American friend.

00:13.143 --> 00:14.318
Man:
I believe in redemption.

00:15.189 --> 00:16.451
Woman:
You've disappointed me.

00:16.625 --> 00:18.018
I can explain this.

00:18.192 --> 00:19.497
Get your hands off.
Hang on a second. Wait.

00:19.671 --> 00:21.456
You know,
I held up my end of things.

00:21.630 --> 00:23.197
And if you'd have done
your part,

00:23.371 --> 00:25.764
none of this
would be happening.

00:25.938 --> 00:29.029
[Crowd chanting]

00:29.159 --> 00:30.291
[Yells]

00:36.079 --> 00:37.907
[Explosions,
gunfire in distance]

00:38.038 --> 00:40.344
[Airplane passing]

00:40.475 --> 00:42.520
[Down-tempo music plays]

00:42.651 --> 00:45.915
[Men shouting in distance]

00:46.046 --> 00:49.832
♪♪

00:49.962 --> 00:51.747
Man:
We need a medic over here!

00:51.877 --> 00:57.144
♪♪

00:57.274 --> 00:59.668
Man: Dixon!

01:01.148 --> 01:03.150
Dixon!

01:03.280 --> 01:06.109
[Crowd chanting indistinctly,
voices echoing]

01:06.240 --> 01:09.852
♪♪

01:09.982 --> 01:11.680
Man: [French accent]
Dixon!

01:11.810 --> 01:14.248
[Crowd chanting]

01:14.378 --> 01:16.685
[Walker snarling]

01:16.815 --> 01:19.688
Codron: Dixon!

01:19.818 --> 01:22.256
Today you die!

01:22.386 --> 01:24.040
For my brother!

01:24.171 --> 01:27.130
[Cheers and applause]

01:27.261 --> 01:29.611
[Dramatic music plays]

01:29.741 --> 01:32.744
♪♪

01:32.875 --> 01:35.051
