28:03.769 --> 28:07.381
<i>♪ Le vent les portera ♪</i>
[Cheers and applause]

28:07.511 --> 28:10.079
♪♪

28:10.210 --> 28:12.647
<i>♪ Génétique en bandoulière ♪</i>

28:12.778 --> 28:15.824
<i>♪ Des chromosomes</i>
<i>dans l'atmosphère ♪</i>

28:15.955 --> 28:18.174
<i>♪ Des taxis pour les galaxies ♪</i>

28:18.305 --> 28:22.439
<i>♪ Et mon tapis volant, dis? ♪</i>

28:22.570 --> 28:24.180
Laurent.

28:25.094 --> 28:26.879
<i>Merci.</i>

28:31.666 --> 28:33.712
Woman:
Isabelle.

28:35.975 --> 28:37.716
[Indistinct conversations]

28:45.201 --> 28:47.116
♪♪

28:47.247 --> 28:49.858
<i>Uh, vous etes</i>
<i>Monsieur Dixon?</i>

28:49.989 --> 28:52.556
His name is Daryl,
and he doesn't speak French.

28:52.687 --> 28:54.167
<i>Ah! Bien sûr.</i>

28:54.297 --> 28:56.560
Uh, the American.
Welcome to the Nest.

28:56.691 --> 28:58.301
I'm Losang.

28:58.432 --> 28:59.433
Are you French?

28:59.563 --> 29:01.261
[Chuckles]
No. Hoboken.

29:01.391 --> 29:02.697
Straight out
of New Jersey.

29:02.828 --> 29:05.613
I came to Paris as a student
in the '90s.

29:05.744 --> 29:07.876
Wow.
Your friend didn't mention that.

29:08.007 --> 29:10.270
That's my dirty
little secret.

29:10.400 --> 29:12.707
Oh, and Azlan?

29:12.838 --> 29:14.622
He didn't make it.

29:14.753 --> 29:17.364
♪♪

29:17.494 --> 29:19.540
He was a good man.

29:19.670 --> 29:22.586
Devoted and kind.

29:22.717 --> 29:25.459
Genet --
She'll be coming for us.

29:25.589 --> 29:29.898
We'll pray not, but if the day
comes, we'll be prepared.

29:30.029 --> 29:31.465
<i>Allons-y, mes amis.</i>
Hmm?

29:34.294 --> 29:36.296
[Indistinct conversations]

29:36.426 --> 29:39.081
