40:13.367 --> 40:15.413
I just heard.

40:16.892 --> 40:18.241
You weren't gonna say
anything?

40:18.372 --> 40:23.508
I made a promise to them,
just like I made to you.

40:24.465 --> 40:27.555
Which you kept,
and I appreciate it.

40:28.948 --> 40:31.603
[Birds crying]

40:36.477 --> 40:38.697
But you also told me
that you left Commonwealth

40:38.827 --> 40:41.700
to see what was out
in the world.

40:41.830 --> 40:44.398
I think you found
something.

40:45.399 --> 40:47.967
Maybe not what you were
looking for, but...

40:48.750 --> 40:52.275
This has always been the story,
ever since I washed ashore here.

40:56.758 --> 40:59.413
What about Laurent?

40:59.544 --> 41:01.894
Are you going to leave
without saying goodbye?

41:02.024 --> 41:05.593
Are you gonna abandon him,
like your father did to you?

41:06.725 --> 41:08.291
This is not that.

41:10.468 --> 41:14.776
I think you care about him...
and I think it scares you.

41:17.605 --> 41:19.738
You think you're escaping
history by doing this,

41:19.868 --> 41:21.740
but you are not.

41:21.870 --> 41:24.351
You're repeating it.

41:26.745 --> 41:28.703
You know, you believe
what you believe,

41:28.834 --> 41:30.749
and I respect you
for that.

41:30.879 --> 41:33.273
And this place feels like home
to you,

41:33.403 --> 41:36.450
and I truly hope it is
for both of you.

41:36.581 --> 41:39.366
But I have my own home
to get back to.

41:42.674 --> 41:44.023
Well, I'm glad we met.

41:45.111 --> 41:47.505
Godspeed on your journey.

41:47.635 --> 41:50.203
[Footsteps echoing]

