52:48.643 --> 52:53.779
♪♪

52:53.909 --> 52:59.001
♪♪

52:59.132 --> 53:01.221
Easy, lady.

53:01.352 --> 53:02.657
Don't kill me.

53:02.788 --> 53:04.093
Where'd you get
the bike?

53:04.224 --> 53:06.270
I swear to God,
I traded some shit for it.

53:06.400 --> 53:08.446
